http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/kozhikode/First-level-test-for-Science-Olympiad/article13983784.ece

: The Regional Science Centre and Planetarium here will conduct the first level test for Kozhikode region for the International Earth Science Olympiad 2016 at 10.30 a.m. on January 16. The 90-minute test is for students of classes 9, 10 and 11. They must have been born after July 1, 1997. The syllabus is Elementary Earth Science, Geography and Astronomy.Candidates can collect the application forms from the Regional Science Centre or download it fromwww.rscpcalicut.org. Candidates will have to obtain the signature of their Principals on the forms and submit it by January 10, with a fee of Rs.50.